<plot>This 16 mm short was created by writers Charles Menville and Len Janson. Menville plays Super Hero Captain Mom who, through a dating service, meets domineering super hero-tamer Kathrin Victor. Love, breakups, contemplated suicide and eventual marriage follow. The final scene is memorable with Victor riding astride Menville as they use Captain Mom power's to soar off on their honeymoon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?093747</url></doc>
